stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> FunctionRegistered: Register Function Definition
    FunctionRegistered --> HandlerRegistered: Register Function Handler
    HandlerRegistered --> RendererRegistered: Register Confirmation Renderer
    
    RendererRegistered --> Ready: All Components Registered
    
    Ready --> FunctionCall: AI requests function
    FunctionCall --> CheckConfirmation: Check requiresConfirmation
    
    CheckConfirmation --> NeedsConfirmation: requiresConfirmation = true
    CheckConfirmation --> DirectExecution: requiresConfirmation = false
    
    NeedsConfirmation --> ShowConfirmation: Get ConfirmationRenderer
    ShowConfirmation --> UserDecision: Display confirmation UI
    
    UserDecision --> Confirmed: User confirms
    UserDecision --> Cancelled: User cancels
    
    Confirmed --> DirectExecution: Proceed with execution
    DirectExecution --> ExecuteFunction: Get FunctionHandler
    ExecuteFunction --> FunctionResult: Execute function
    
    FunctionResult --> [*]: Complete
    Cancelled --> [*]: Cancelled